flowchart TD
    Start([Inicio]) --> Basics[basics · universal]
    Basics --> Q1{Q1 · race_focus}

    Q1 -->|first_5k / first_race| BranchFirst[🟢 Branch: Primeira Prova]
    Q1 -->|improve_5k| Branch5K[🔵 Branch: Evoluidor 5K]
    Q1 -->|improve_10k| Branch10K[🔵 Branch: Evoluidor 10K]

    BranchFirst --> Q2
    Branch5K --> Q2
    Branch10K --> Q2

    Q2[Q2 · training_frequency] --> Q3[Q3 · biggest_barrier]
    Q3 --> Q4{Q4 · uses_gps}

    Q4 -->|yes_watch / yes_phone| Q5[Q5 · recent_pace]
    Q4 -->|no_gps| Q6

    Q5 --> Q6{Q6 · health_conditions}

    Q6 -->|none / respiratory / diabetes / recent_sedentary| PN
    Q6 -->|cardiac / joint_injury| Safety[🚨 safetyReduced]
    Safety --> PN

    PN[personal_note · universal] --> Goal[goal · universal]
    Goal --> Contact[contact · universal]
    Contact --> End([relatorio IA])

